name: Miniature Porcelain Plate by Cheryl Ewing
description:
Ambiguous stories are pieced together from selections of photographs letter, and other vintage paper sources. 

Speckles of glaze are used to highlight areas and allow for gold luster application. Seemingly random glistens adorn the surface, representing fond memories that can live on and be kept preserved on the porcelain surface.

This miniature ceramic plate measure's just under 4 inches, hang it on a wall, sit it on fire place, where ever it finds it's place it will have found it's home .

***please note the smaller plate is not included although can be found to buy here on our site.

name: Bear cuff by Made by Daisy
description:
This unique cuff bracelet of the Grizzly Bear has a lovely cosy feel to it.

The image has been printed onto a special paper, which is slightly translucent and allows some of the brass to show through. 
This gives gives the bracelets more character. It's then sealed with a layer of hard-wearing resin to protect it - although I would advise not to get it soaking wet!

 1.5 inches wide (approx 38mm).
 6 inches in length (152mm) with an opening of around 1 inch (25mm) – The bracelets are easily adjustable to fit most wrist sizes.

name: Oh Floral Heart 13" x 19" Limited Edition Digital Print by The Aviary
description:
A beautiful, unframed, limited edition print of a collection of fallen roses in the shape of a heart.
This edition of just fifty fine art prints has been made from an original illustration, delicately drawn and coloured by Victoria in The Aviary studios within the heart of the Kent countryside.

A perfect addition to the home for nature lovers, newly weds, or a truly lovely gift for Valentine's Day.

Each print is signed and dated by the artist, and comes wrapped in cellophane, rolled and shipped to you in a tube .

Made from: 
Printed in full colour on archival, acid-free Somerset cotton rag paper stock.

Dimensions: 
13 x 19 inches / 48.26cm x 33cm
